//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
AFFINE CIPHER
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

Easy stuff. We do freq. analysis on the ciphertext. We only need to figure out
2 of the mappings (ie. a = g, y = d) and then solve a simultaneous equation.

